title: 01/05/21 - HOUR 1 - Ian Rapoport
itunes:title: 01/05/21 - HOUR 1 - Ian Rapoport
description:
Dan discusses the continued fallout from Washington and the Eagles, and reacts to Giants coach Joe Judge's disgust at the game. Dan says the Giants need to move on. He also talks with Ian Rapoport about the head coach openings in the NFL.
